{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"lifecycle000","type":"group","x":-380,"y":200,"width":1200,"height":700,"color":"5","label":"核心迭代循环 - 8 阶段生命周期"},
		{"id":"title001","type":"text","text":"# Autoresearch 深度分析\n\n**插件式 Claude Code Skill**：1 核心 + 8 子命令 + 1 规划向导\n目标驱动的自主迭代系统","x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":120,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"arch001","type":"text","text":"## 整体架构\n\n```\nautoresearch (插件)\n├── /autoresearch (核心)\n├── /autoresearch:plan (规划)\n├── /autoresearch:debug (调试)\n├── /autoresearch:fix (修复)\n├── /autoresearch:security\n├── /autoresearch:ship (发布)\n├── /autoresearch:scenario\n├── /autoresearch:predict\n└── /autoresearch:learn\n```","x":-800,"y":200,"width":320,"height":360,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"phase0","type":"text","text":"### Phase 0: 前置检查\n\n- Git 仓库验证\n- 工作区干净检查\n- Lock 文件检查\n- HEAD 状态检查\n- Git hooks 检查\n\n**失败 → 停止**\n**警告 → 谨慎继续**","x":-350,"y":280,"width":240,"height":200,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"phase1","type":"text","text":"### Phase 1: 回顾\n\n每次迭代必做：\n1. 读取文件当前状态\n2. 读取结果日志\n3. `git log --oneline -20`\n4. `git diff HEAD~1`\n5. 识别成功/失败/未尝试\n6. 检查迭代次数\n\n**Git = 记忆**","x":-70,"y":280,"width":240,"height":200,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"phase2","type":"text","text":"### Phase 2: 构思\n\n战略性选择：\n1. 修复上次崩溃\n2. 利用成功案例\n3. 探索新方法\n4. 组合成功方案\n5. 简化代码\n6. 激进实验\n\n**反模式**：重复失败变更","x":210,"y":280,"width":240,"height":200,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"phase3","type":"text","text":"### Phase 3: 修改\n\n**原子性变更**：\n- 一次一个变更\n- 一句话测试\n- 单意图验证\n\n自检：\n```bash\nFILES_CHANGED=$(git diff \\\n  --name-only | wc -l)\n```\n\n超过 5 个文件 → 审查","x":490,"y":280,"width":240,"height":200,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"phase4","type":"text","text":"### Phase 4: 提交\n\n**验证前提交**：\n```bash\ngit add <file1> <file2>\ngit commit -m \n  \"experiment(<scope>): \n   <description>\"\n```\n\nHook 失败处理：\n1. 理解错误\n2. 修复重试\n3. 记录回滚\n\n**禁止 --no-verify**","x":770,"y":280,"width":240,"height":200,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"phase5","type":"text","text":"### Phase 5: 验证\n\n运行验证命令 + 指标提取\n\n**噪声处理**：\n- 多轮验证取中位数\n- 最小改进阈值\n- 确认运行\n\n**验证命令模板**：\n- Node.js: Jest coverage\n- Python: pytest --cov\n- Rust: cargo test\n- Go: go test","x":-350,"y":520,"width":240,"height":220,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"combo001","type":"text","text":"## 组合使用模式\n\n### 1. 独立使用\n每个子命令可独立调用\n\n### 2. 链式组合\n```bash\n/autoresearch:predict \\\n  --chain debug,fix,ship\n```\n\n### 3. 迭代组合\n在主循环中使用其他工具作为验证\n\n### 典型场景\n\n**发布前安全审查**：\n```bash\npredict --chain security\nsecurity --fix --fail-on critical\nship --auto\n```\n\n**新功能质量保证**：\n```bash\nscenario --depth deep\npredict --chain debug\nfix\nlearn --mode update\nship --monitor 10\n```\n\n**代码库健康检查**：\n```bash\nlearn --mode check\ndebug\nsecurity --diff\nfix\nlearn --mode update\n```","x":900,"y":200,"width":420,"height":480,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"phase55","type":"text","text":"### Phase 5.5: 守卫\n\n**回归检查**（可选）\n\n验证 vs 守卫：\n- 验证：指标改进了吗？\n- 守卫：其他东西坏了吗？\n\n**守卫失败恢复**：\n最多 2 次重新优化尝试\n1. 回滚\n2. 分析守卫输出\n3. 重新优化\n4. 重新验证","x":-70,"y":520,"width":240,"height":220,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"phase6","type":"text","text":"### Phase 6: 决策\n\n**无歧义规则**：\n\n```bash\n指标提升 AND 无守卫:\n  STATUS = \"keep\"\n指标提升 AND 守卫失败:\n  safe_revert() + 重试\n指标下降:\n  STATUS = \"discard\"\n  safe_revert()\n崩溃:\n  STATUS = \"crash\"\n  safe_revert()\n```","x":210,"y":520,"width":240,"height":220,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"phase7","type":"text","text":"### Phase 7: 记录\n\n追加到结果日志（TSV）：\n\n```\niteration|commit|\n  metric|delta|\n  guard|status|\n  description\n```\n\n**有效状态**：\n- keep\n- keep (reworked)\n- discard\n- crash\n- no-op\n- hook-blocked","x":490,"y":520,"width":240,"height":220,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"phase8","type":"text","text":"### Phase 8: 重复\n\n**无界模式**：永不停止\n\n**有界模式** (Iterations: N)：\n```\nif current < max:\n  进入 Phase 1\nif 达到目标:\n  停止 + 总结\n```\n\n**卡住时**（>5 连续丢弃）：\n1. 重新读取文件\n2. 审查结果日志\n3. 组合成功变更\n4. 尝试激进变更","x":770,"y":520,"width":240,"height":220,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"commands001","type":"text","text":"## 八大子命令\n\n### 1. `/autoresearch` - 核心\n通用目标驱动优化\n\n### 2. `/autoresearch:plan`\n规划向导：目标→配置\n\n### 3. `/autoresearch:debug`\nBug 狩猎：科学方法\n\n### 4. `/autoresearch:fix`\n错误修复：迭代修复\n\n### 5. `/autoresearch:security`\n安全审计：STRIDE + OWASP\n\n### 6. `/autoresearch:ship`\n发布工作流：8 阶段\n\n### 7. `/autoresearch:scenario`\n场景生成：12 维度探索\n\n### 8. `/autoresearch:predict`\n多角色预测：群体智能\n\n### 9. `/autoresearch:learn`\n文档引擎：自动生成","x":-800,"y":620,"width":380,"height":400,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"principles001","type":"text","text":"## 七条核心原则\n\n### 1. 约束 = 赋能\n自治通过有意约束成功，而非尽管有约束\n\n### 2. 分离策略与战术\n人类设定方向，代理执行迭代\n\n### 3. 指标必须机械\n如果不能用命令验证，就不能自主迭代\n\n### 4. 验证必须快\n快速验证支持迭代，慢验证杀死迭代\n\n### 5. 迭代成本塑造行为\n便宜迭代 → 大胆探索\n昂贵迭代 → 保守行为\n\n### 6. Git 是记忆和审计跟踪\n每次成功变更都提交 → 因果跟踪 + 堆叠胜利\n\n### 7. 诚实限制\n说明系统能做什么和不能做什么","x":-800,"y":1080,"width":620,"height":480,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"config001","type":"text","text":"## 关键配置参数\n\n### 循环模式\n- 无 `Iterations`：无界模式\n- `Iterations: N`：有界模式\n\n### 验证相关\n- `Verify`：提取指标命令\n- `Guard`：回归测试命令\n- `Noise: high`：多轮验证\n- `Min-Delta: X`：最小改进阈值\n\n### 原子性配置\n- `Atomicity: strict`：严格模式\n- `Atomicity: relaxed`：宽松模式\n- `Max-Files-Per-Change: N`\n\n### Git 记忆配置\n- `Memory-Depth: N`\n- `Diff-Review: HEAD~N`","x":-120,"y":1080,"width":340,"height":480,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"output001","type":"text","text":"## 输出产物\n\n每次运行创建**带时间戳的输出目录**：\n\n```\nautoresearch-results.tsv\nsecurity/{YYMMDD}-{HHMM}-{slug}/\n├── overview.md\n├── threat-model.md\n├── attack-surface-map.md\n├── findings.md\n└── security-audit-results.tsv\n\nship/{YYMMDD}-{HHMM}-{slug}/\n├── checklist.md\n├── ship-log.tsv\n└── summary.md\n\nscenario/{YYMMDD}-{HHMM}-{slug}/\npredict/{YYMMDD}-{HHMM}-{slug}/\nlearn/{YYMMDD}-{HHMM}-{slug}/\n```","x":280,"y":1080,"width":400,"height":480,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"domain001","type":"text","text":"## 领域适配\n\n| 领域 | 指标 | 验证命令 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| 后端代码 | 测试覆盖率 | npm test |\n| 前端 UI | Lighthouse | npx lighthouse |\n| ML 训练 | val_loss | uv run train.py |\n| 性能 | 基准时间(ms) | npm run bench |\n| 重构 | LOC 减少 | npm test && wc -l |\n| 安全 | OWASP 覆盖率 | /autoresearch:security |\n| 发布 | 检查清单通过率 | /autoresearch:ship |\n| 调试 | Bug 发现数 | /autoresearch:debug |\n| 修复 | 错误数 | /autoresearch:fix |\n| 场景分析 | 场景覆盖分数 | /autoresearch:scenario |\n| 预测 | 发现数 | /autoresearch:predict |\n| 文档 | 验证通过率 | /autoresearch:learn |\n\n**适配循环到你的领域。原则是通用的；指标是领域特定的。**","x":740,"y":1080,"width":480,"height":480,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"summary001","type":"text","text":"## 总结\n\n**Autoresearch 是一个高度模块化、可组合的自动化工具系统**，核心是**基于 Git 记忆的自主迭代循环**。\n\n**关键特点**：🎯 目标驱动 | 🔄 自动迭代 | 🛡️ 安全机制 | 📊 可验证 | 🧠 Git 记忆 | 🧩 模块化 | 🔗 可组合\n\n**核心理念**：\n> 自治在你约束范围、明确成功、机械化验证，并让代理优化战术而人类优化策略时扩展。\n> 这不是\"移除人类\"。这是重新分配人类努力从执行到方向。人类通过专注于不可简化的创造性/战略性工作变得更有价值。","x":-800,"y":1620,"width":1420,"height":240,"color":"6"}
	],
